1
00:00:07,599 --> 00:00:08,720
Zhai Qiuyu

2
00:00:09,320 --> 00:00:10,199
How are you?

3
00:00:18,079 --> 00:00:18,879
Who is he?

4
00:00:23,039 --> 00:00:24,440
This is Brother Qiuyu's physiotherapist

5
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,600
Li Youen, professor Li

6
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:28,280
What are you doing here?

7
00:00:29,839 --> 00:00:31,039
So many years without seeing each other

8
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,039
Haven't you even missed me?

9
00:00:35,799 --> 00:00:36,880
I came specially

10
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:38,200
What do you want from me?

11
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:42,039
this bad temper

12
00:00:42,359 --> 00:00:43,479
How have you not changed it?

13
00:00:45,039 --> 00:00:46,439
There is an exhibition of sculptures

14
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:48,439
I have to prepare a decent work

15
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:50,280
Originally

16
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,359
I wanted to talk to you

17
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,240
but now

18
00:01:04,079 --> 00:01:05,480
What a familiar smell

19
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,640
Would you be interested in being my model?

20
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:12,719
¿You?

21
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,840
Are you kidding?

22
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,239
I'm very serious

23
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,840
since seven minutes ago

24
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,480
since I saw you for the first time

25
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,959
you have attracted me

26
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:22,000
Zhou Song

27
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,879
So I was wondering

28
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,079
a person as wonderful as you

29
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:28,640
how could he be next to Zhai Qiuyu?

30
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,480
And what are you still doing standing?

31
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,680
Aren't we going to train?

32
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,680
Gu Hao

33
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:40,560
Aren't we going to take a photo?

34
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:49,040
see you later

35
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,359
Professor Li

36
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:53,159
Hermano Qiuyu

37
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,400
Your friend is very pretty

38
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,080
Who is it?

39
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,279
Did you forget about me so soon?

40
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,519
De Zhai Qiuyu.

41
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,600
Professor Li.

42
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,879
I am not

43
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,439
Zhai Qiuyu is not here.

44
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,560
Us

45
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,720
We are not always together either.

46
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,560
I didn't come looking for him.

47
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,759
I came to look

48
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:52,800
the Musa.

49
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:54,360
¿Musa?

50
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,639
Does it have to do with reserve dyeing?

51
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:03,040
The color or the shape?

52
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:05,279
Neither of them.

53
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,759
Don't you want to know what I found?

54
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:34,480
I don't know the needs of an artist

55
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,199
But if she is a Muse

56
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,800
It must be something wonderful

57
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:43,120
It certainly is wonderful

58
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,959
What are you looking at?

59
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:03,160
The light in you

60
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:06,199
That's the Muse I've been searching for

61
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,360
Luz

62
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,600
Luz

63
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:12,480
That serene air that you have

64
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,680
in the light

65
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:16,360
Reveals an untamed form

66
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,600
How to say it?

67
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,240
Like clay in my studio

68
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,079
Suave

69
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,439
And at the same time firm

70
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,519
what you say

71
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,279
It's me

72
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,279
Li Youen

73
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,759
Are you leaving so early today?

74
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,480
I have something to do

75
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,240
I have to go to the mall

76
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:11,000
Which one will Xiao Si like more?

77
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,839
We meet again.

78
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,680
Professor Li.

79
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,639
What a coincidence that we see each other.

80
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,120
Professor Zhou.

81
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,920
How come...

82
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,000
...are you coming to look for inspiration again?

83
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:34,680
This time

84
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:37,680
You come to watch people.

85
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,480
Gracias.

86
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,480
This one above is fine.

87
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,680
I have to go

88
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,720
Leave

89
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,639
Until next time

90
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:35,480
Boss

91
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,720
How much does this cost?

92
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,720
This toy set

93
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,720
The tall man from before already paid

94
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,039
He already paid

95
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:41,639
Yeah

96
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:43,120
This car was also paid for

97
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:01,480
Zhai Qiuyu

98
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,720
What are these things?

99
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,840
They are toys I bought for a friend.

100
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:13,879
Immature.

101
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:19,960
I'll take them tomorrow.

102
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:46,279
Good afternoon.

103
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,360
Professor Li.

104
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:56,120
We meet a lot lately.

105
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:57,360
This time,

106
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,879
It's no longer a coincidence, right?

107
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:05,679
Professor Zhou

108
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,120
I really can't accept it

109
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,399
And the toys from last time

110
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,360
How much do they cost?

111
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,679
I have to give it back to you

112
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:11,879
give me a chance

113
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,399
Let me bribe you a little

114
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:14,559
my model

115
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,000
Professor Zhou

116
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,440
I didn't joke

117
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,320
I'm really not suitable

118
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,159
There is no one more suitable than you

119
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:25,039
I want to capture your indomitable side

120
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:26,559
The sculpture

121
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,919
It is the most direct way

122
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,440
to turn instant beauty into something eternal

123
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:32,960
That is

124
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,639
my selfish motivation

125
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,759
Zhai Qiuyu

126
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,440
He will not agree

127
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:58,320
He doesn't like you and me

128
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:00,679
let's be so close

129
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,879
Do you care a lot

130
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:06,320
lo que sienta Zhai Qiuyu?

131
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,159
Zhai Qiuyu

132
00:11:25,879 --> 00:11:27,200
Are you going to raise goldfish?

133
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,639
He says that

134
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,759
every time a goldfish moves its tail

135
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:35,759
uses the strength of his entire trunk

136
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,919
Tens of thousands of tail movements a day

137
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:40,440
Every time you have to use your trunk strength

138
00:11:42,679 --> 00:11:44,679
Can you guess what his tail is doing?

139
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,480
Won't there also be damage accumulated over years?

140
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,039
When did you become so lazy?

141
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:02,320
And did you start researching art?

142
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:05,039
Do you bring home ugly things every day?

143
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,480
I didn't buy them.

144
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:10,639
I met Professor Zhou on the way.

145
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,279
He gave them to me.

146
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,720
Why would I give you things?

147
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,840
He gave them to many people.

148
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,799
He said he wanted to gather opinions from viewers.

149
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:10,960
Professor Li

150
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:13,679
Flower season is almost over

151
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:29,159
Locked me up

152
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,159
Professor Li

153
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,639
I feel very dizzy

154
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,080
My throat hurts too

155
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,120
Alright

156
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,679
I admit that maybe I faked it a little

157
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,840
To gain your sympathy

158
00:13:43,399 --> 00:13:44,200
So

159
00:13:44,679 --> 00:13:47,039
Could you come see me after work?

160
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:48,559
I will go too

161
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,240
I'll buy you a cupcake

162
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,960
Zhai Qiuyu is really lucky

163
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,360
drink water

164
00:15:03,159 --> 00:15:04,039
is it still hot?

165
00:15:28,639 --> 00:15:29,879
They were caught red-handed

166
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,279
that image

167
00:15:36,559 --> 00:15:38,360
It's been on my mind for a long time.

168
00:15:39,159 --> 00:15:41,120
but I could never capture its essence

169
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:43,639
I don't know what face he has

170
00:15:44,159 --> 00:15:46,080
Until that day on the tree-lined path

171
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,159
you see

172
00:15:59,879 --> 00:16:01,840
From the beginning I told the truth

173
00:16:02,879 --> 00:16:04,320
I wanted you to be my model

174
00:16:05,039 --> 00:16:05,840
But

175
00:16:06,519 --> 00:16:07,799
no one believed me

176
00:16:14,399 --> 00:16:15,200
Li Youen

177
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:19,720
I see a very faint sadness in you

178
00:16:20,759 --> 00:16:21,559
I guess

179
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,240
that you lost something very valuable

180
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:28,080
That's why

181
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:31,240
you are afraid of losing him again at any moment

182
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:36,840
Yeah

183
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,200
I am very afraid of losing my brother

184
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,120
being sincere

185
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,200
I admire you a lot

186
00:16:52,919 --> 00:16:53,720
Even

187
00:16:55,759 --> 00:16:56,759
I have some greed

188
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,159
Yo

189
00:16:58,919 --> 00:16:59,919
What are you two talking about?

190
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,519
I agree to be your model

191
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,200
I'm going too

192
00:17:25,279 --> 00:17:26,319
close your eyes

193
00:17:27,279 --> 00:17:30,440
Imagine the fear and helplessness of losing everything

194
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,240
Now

195
00:17:44,359 --> 00:17:47,319
you have enough strength to accept it

196
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,720
to comfort you

197
00:18:04,079 --> 00:18:04,880
That's how it is

198
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,400
Quick, take the photo!

199
00:18:08,759 --> 00:18:09,519
Professor Li

200
00:18:09,519 --> 00:18:10,519
look at me

201
00:18:26,119 --> 00:18:27,039
You have done very well

202
00:18:27,039 --> 00:18:27,640
Professor Li

203
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,880
How can I thank you?

204
00:18:36,559 --> 00:18:37,440
No, no, no.

205
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,400
I'm glad I could help you.

206
00:18:40,559 --> 00:18:42,599
How about I give you ten more Lego sets?

207
00:18:42,839 --> 00:18:44,480
If you don't need anything else.

208
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,000
I don't like it anymore.

209
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,799
No problem.

210
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,599
Then I will give them to you one by one.

211
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,599
Until you are satisfied.

212
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,119
Do you like goldfish?

213
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,359
Yeah.

214
00:19:19,799 --> 00:19:20,599
Thank you so much

215
00:19:20,599 --> 00:19:21,359
Little Gu Hao

216
00:19:21,519 --> 00:19:23,039
You are so busy and yet you come out to help me take photos

217
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,119
Don't worry, Professor Zhou

218
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,319
I also think it's very interesting

219
00:19:25,559 --> 00:19:26,720
I look forward to your work

220
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,839
If there is anything else I can help with

221
00:19:28,839 --> 00:19:29,720
just call me

222
00:19:29,799 --> 00:19:30,680
Whenever?

223
00:19:32,039 --> 00:19:34,240
So in a couple of days, can you help me carry dirt home?

224
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:34,920
Of course

225
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:39,640
look at this

226
00:19:52,559 --> 00:19:53,200
It's almost gone

227
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,640
I could have thrown the camera in the water

228
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,599
I was too reckless

229
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:58,359
If I call someone to come fix it

230
00:19:58,759 --> 00:19:59,920
will it be faster?

231
00:20:00,279 --> 00:20:01,079
No problem

232
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,319
I can

233
00:20:02,799 --> 00:20:04,759
Thank goodness he wasn't in the water for long.

234
00:20:05,119 --> 00:20:06,119
and your house is close

235
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,519
I'm worried about the inside photos

236
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,960
It's nothing serious

237
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:18,960
Don't repair it

238
00:20:19,759 --> 00:20:21,079
I'll buy you a new one later

239
00:20:21,599 --> 00:20:22,400
No problem

240
00:20:22,599 --> 00:20:23,559
I can fix it

241
00:20:53,119 --> 00:20:55,319
Have you been working at Zhai Qiuyu's club?

242
00:20:55,319 --> 00:20:57,319
I did an internship at the club when I was at university

243
00:21:03,039 --> 00:21:03,839
Professor Zhou

244
00:21:04,759 --> 00:21:06,039
Do you live alone?

245
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:08,839
You and Li Youen

246
00:21:09,359 --> 00:21:10,480
have you known each other for a long time?

247
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:11,400
No

248
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,160
Professor Li is a new colleague

249
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,759
I haven't worked with him many days

250
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:19,960
But

251
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,759
he and brother Qiu Yu seem very close

252
00:21:24,079 --> 00:21:25,440
So close that

253
00:21:27,319 --> 00:21:28,200
they look like a couple

254
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,759
Para Li Youen

255
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,839
It is already something obvious to everyone

256
00:21:45,319 --> 00:21:46,119
Why don't you ask

257
00:21:46,119 --> 00:21:47,680
What relationship do I have with Brother Qiu Yu?

258
00:21:49,559 --> 00:21:50,599
So you with him

259
00:21:50,759 --> 00:21:51,880
what relationship do you have?

260
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:53,920
The relationship between fans and idols...

261
00:21:54,079 --> 00:21:55,400
I followed my idol to the club.

262
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,319
Everyone knows it.

263
00:21:56,759 --> 00:21:58,119
When I entered college for the first time,

264
00:21:58,160 --> 00:22:00,279
It was watching Qiu Yu Ge's matches that got me into tennis.

265
00:22:00,279 --> 00:22:00,920
That's why,

266
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,720
I even joined my school's tennis club.

267
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:04,319
Although I'm not good at playing tennis.

268
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,240
But in the tennis club

269
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:06,400
I met many good friends.

270
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,920
I'm done talking

271
00:22:31,839 --> 00:22:32,759
It was great

272
00:22:33,319 --> 00:22:34,279
Tired of talking?

273
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,240
Eat a dragon fruit

274
00:22:36,359 --> 00:22:37,279
rest a little

275
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,559
Professor Zhou

276
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:46,279
Do you live alone?

277
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,759
Actually

278
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:56,720
I received a work call

279
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:58,200
Stay alone for a while

280
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:02,599
If it's only been a few days

281
00:24:03,079 --> 00:24:04,799
you have called me eight hundred times

282
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,200
But you don't answer either!

283
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:08,160
If we haven't seen each other for a month

284
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,680
and you don't even give me a clear answer

285
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,440
What do you want, seriously?

286
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:12,839
Oh, oh, oh

287
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:13,880
stop pouting

288
00:24:14,559 --> 00:24:15,920
Then I'll buy you a Prada

289
00:24:16,599 --> 00:24:18,079
Are you trying to trick me again?

290
00:24:18,279 --> 00:24:20,079
If you say that, I'm going to be sad

291
00:24:20,559 --> 00:24:21,799
Originally, I wanted to finish quickly

292
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:23,279
so I can dedicate myself to you

293
00:24:24,079 --> 00:24:25,079
Only you say that

294
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:28,480
Dear

295
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:30,759
When it's over, I'll tell you

